properties.Name: FinancialBudget
properties.Description: The financial budget is a financial means for analyzing the financial condition of a business in terms of assets, liabilities, cash flow, working capital and profitability.

Columns.Name: FinancialBudgetId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Financial Budget.

Columns.Name: FinancialBudgetVersionId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Financial Budget Version.

Columns.Name: MasterBudgetId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Master Budget.

Columns.Name: MasterBudgetVersionId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Master Budget Version.

Columns.Name: PartyId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Party.

Columns.Name: OrganizationId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an organization.

Columns.Name: BeginningCashBalanceAmount
Columns.Description: The amount of cash at the beginning of the period.

Columns.Name: PlannedReceiptsFromCustomersAmount
Columns.Description: The planned total of receipts to be collected from customers as of the indicated date.

Columns.Name: ActualReceiptsFromCustomersAmount
Columns.Description: The actual total receipts collected from customers as of the indicated date.

Columns.Name: PlannedTotalDisbursementsAmount
Columns.Description: The planned total cash disbursements as of the indicated date.

Columns.Name: ActualTotalDisbursementsAmount
Columns.Description: The actual total cash disbursements as of the indicated date.

Columns.Name: PlannedTotalCashAvailableAmount
Columns.Description: The planned total cash to be available as of the indicated date.

Columns.Name: ActualTotalCashAvailableAmount
Columns.Description: The actual total cash available as of the indicated date.

Columns.Name: PlannedTotalFinancingAmount
Columns.Description: The planned total financing disbursements amount as of the indicated date.

Columns.Name: ActualTotalFinancingAmount
Columns.Description: The actual total financing disbursements amount as of the indicated date.

Columns.Name: CashBalanceAmount
Columns.Description: The actual cash  balance for the associated date.

Columns.Name: SalesRevenueAmount
Columns.Description: The amount of sales revenues.

Columns.Name: TotalVariablesExpensesAmount
Columns.Description: The total variable expenses amount.

Columns.Name: TotalFixedExpensesAmount
Columns.Description: The total amount of fixed expenses.

Columns.Name: NetOperatingIncomeAmount
Columns.Description: The net operating income amount.

Columns.Name: InterestExpenseAmount
Columns.Description: The amount of interest expenses to be subtracted from net operating income = Net Income Before Taxes Amount

Columns.Name: NetIncomeBeforeTaxesAmount
Columns.Description: Net Income before taxes.

Columns.Name: IncomeTaxesAmount
Columns.Description: Income taxes amount due to be applied to Net Income Before Taxes.

Columns.Name: NetIncomeAmount
Columns.Description: Net Income after taxes.
